---
title: Double Mild Sri Lankan Beef Coconut Curry with Basmati Rice & Mint
description: Tender beef strips are tossed in a rich, Sri Lankan-spiced curry sauce for an explosion of flavour. This hearty, warming bowl of goodness is a 10 out of 10 in our eyes, with fragrant mint to add the perfect pop of brightness
